cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the detection of local blur in images. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also extensively uses deep neural networks, which are a popular tool in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of blur maps in magnification, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the segmentation of blur regions, which is related to graphics (cs.GR).
